---
// FAQ Section Component
---

<!--  FAQ Section -->
<section class="faq py-5 py-lg-11 py-xl-12">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-5 gap-xl-11">
      <div class="row gap-7 gap-xl-0">
        <div class="col-xl-4 col-xxl-4">
          <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-7 py-2" data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-delay="100"
            data-aos-duration="1000">
            <span
              class="round-36 flex-shrink-0 text-dark rounded-circle bg-primary hstack justify-content-center fw-medium">08</span>
            <hr class="border-line bg-white">
            <span class="badge text-bg-dark">FAQs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xl-8 col-xxl-7">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xxl-9">
              <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100"
                data-aos-duration="1000">
                <h2 class="mb-0">Your Questions, Answered</h2>
                <p class="fs-5 mb-0 text-opacity-70">We believe in transparency. Here are answers to common questions about our process and the technology we use.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row justify-content-end">
        <div class="col-xl-8">
          <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200"
            data-aos-duration="1000">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-8 fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#flush-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseOne">
                  Why do you use open-source tools like SuiteCRM instead of popular SaaS products?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="flush-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                <div class="accordion-body pt-0 fs-5 text-dark">We believe in giving you full control and ownership of your data. Open-source tools eliminate vendor lock-in, significantly lower your long-term software costs, and offer limitless flexibility to build a stack that perfectly fits your business processes.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-8 fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#flush-collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseTwo">
                  How does the 'AI-powered' part work? Is it safe for my business?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="flush-collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                <div class="accordion-body pt-0 fs-5 text-dark">It's completely safe because we operate on a 'human-in-the-loop' principle. Our AI agents handle tasks like summarizing emails or scoring leads, but they only create drafts and suggestions. A human from your team always gives the final approval before any action is taken.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-8 fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#flush-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseThree">
                  How long does a typical project take to go live?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="flush-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                <div class="accordion-body pt-0 fs-5 text-dark">Our process is designed for speed. For a standard stack setup, you can expect to be live and operational within three weeks. We deliver value in weeks, not months.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-8 fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#flush-collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseFour">
                  Is this service a good fit for my small team?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="flush-collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                <div class="accordion-body pt-0 fs-5 text-dark">Absolutely. Our lean stack is specifically designed for small to medium-sized businesses and teams that feel overwhelmed by too many scattered tools. If you value simplicity, clear data, and smart automation, you are a perfect fit.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed fs-8 fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#flush-collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseFive">
                  What if I only need one part of the service, like an automation workflow?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="flush-collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                <div class="accordion-body pt-0 fs-5 text-dark">While the all-in-one stack provides the most value, we are flexible. Services like building a specific AI agent, setting up email deliverability, or cleaning up your existing CRM can be scoped as smaller, standalone projects.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>